Transport Icons for Windows 10

Transport icons for Windows 10 are designed to match the original icons of Windows 10; we’ve summarized this design system in our article that Microsoft has failed to produce. Optimized for 32×32 pixels, these are our cleanest outline icons, only to compete with our small 1em icons and way less detailed as our iOS icons. Like all our free icon packs, these Transport icons are available for download as PNG, SVG, PDF and other vectors, as an icon font, and as HTML/CSS snippets.

Transport Icons for iOS

These are the Transport icons for iOS. They follow the iOS Human Interface Guidelines (Apple could have done it better though), first introduced in iOS 7 and supported in all later releases up until now (at least iOS 11). These are outline icons; they're based on thin two-pixel lines and is optimized for 50×50 pixels. If you're creating an iOS app, either download Transport PNG icons in 3 sizes (free icons for 50 and 100px; for folks who paid there's 150px) or download a single vector icon in PDF format (you'll have to buy icons) — Xcode will generate the proper PNGs on the compilation. There's a matching set of glyph icons — Apple introduced them in iOS 11 and uses for tab bars.

Transport Glyphs Icons

Apple introduced the glyph icons in iOS 11 and uses them for tab bar (along with regular iOS icons that are for everything else). The grid is 30×30 pixels. Unlike original iOS icons which are the outline ones, these icons consist of the the filled shapes and visually dense. If you're creating an iOS app, either download Transport PNG icons in 3 sizes (free icons for 50 and 100px; for folks who paid there's 150px) or download a single vector icon in PDF format (you'll have to buy icons) — Xcode will generate the proper PNGs on the compilation.

1em, Small Transport Icons

These small, tiny Transport icons are designed to fit the text. They are only 16 pixels tall, thus we called them 1em (1em=16px). The problem that web designers are aware: once inserted in text, the icons break the line, making text “dance” and overall make design look chaotic. 1em is the only icon pack that follows the text, i.e. looks natural in a line of text of a standard font size. Of course, you can scale it up for larger text. A good idea is to generate a font and use it along with your text (we have a built-in font generator). Enjoy your new, clean menus, action buttons, and other pieces of text combined with an icon.

Transport Icons for Metro

Nós desenhamos os Transport ícones de Metro de acordo com o guia de ferramentas para ícones da Microsoft De acordo com a espicificação da Microsoft, nós otimizamos eles para grade de 26×26, assim encorajamos você a usá-los em 26×26 ou 52×52; alguns dos ícones ficarão bem em 13×13 (tenha cuidado). Há um estilo de visual novo da Microsoft, Windows 10. Ainda sim, Metro é válido para esses stiles, essas cores na caixa de menu inicial. Finalmente, ele é meramente um estilo bonito, especialmente para pessoas normais que não leem guias de design para sistemas operacionais no café da manhã.
